Usage: deselectNet [-help] [<net>*] [-clock | -nonDefaultRule | -shield]

-help               # Prints out the command usage
<net>*              # Specify the net name ((net)*, optional)
-clock              # Select all nets that have a DEF attribute "USE CLOCK" 
                    # (bool, optional)
-nonDefaultRule     # Select all nets that have a DEF attribute "USE
                    # NONDEFAULTRULE" (bool, optional)
-shield             # Select all nets that have a DEF attribute "USE
                    # SHIELDNETS" (bool, optional)